      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;transmutation&nbsp;[cold, evil, water];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;cleric/oracle 2, inquisitor 2;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (a flask of unholy water or 5 pounds of powdered silver worth 25 gp)<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;0 feet<br>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Effect</strong>&nbsp;one ice weapon<br>\n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 minute/level (D)<br>\n      <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;none;&nbsp;\n      <strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;no<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell functions as <i>holy ice weapon</i>, except the weapon is made of frozen unholy water, and instead deals additional damage to creatures that are susceptible to unholy water.</p>\n</div>\n",
